{"tid":1992873,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【抗暴之戰】葵芳11.11撞人交警傳獲晉升 許智峯促鄧炳強核實身份","createTime":"2020-04-28T11:36:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-28T11:53:12.000Z","uid":17646,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f1c7700bc594ed611bb942ffb4d919efcdbda82e","tid":1992873,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T11:36:32.000Z","msg":"一名交通警員去年11月11日在葵芳多次駕電單車高速衝向人群，立法會議員許智峯昨日（28日）去信警務處處長鄧炳強，要求確認撞人警員身份，以供日後提出訴訟。消息指，該警員為時任新界南交通部執行及管制組吳姓警長，近月更獲晉升為警署警長。許智峯指，接獲的3個消息來源均指向同一人，希望鄧炳強可核實資料，否則不排除對外公開，以尋找更多線索。<br />\n<br />\n其他內文請入蘋果度睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200428/JOQXQ5UUZ6XSGMUC5SWISBZPGM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200428%2FJOQXQ5UUZ6XSGMUC5SWISBZPGM%2F&d=mbsn9%2Fi9gU9wZYjOUdyYPkn12mAFq1syGW6OSBl8LUM%3D&h=c506a2d9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200428%2FJOQXQ5UUZ6XSGMUC5SWISBZPGM%2F&h=52ec34a1\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200428/JOQXQ5UUZ6XSGMUC5SWISBZPGM/</a>"},{"pid":"d29e0d6cc8577ea025403dafc04e622753b92490","tid":1992873,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T11:39:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a6aa880f5ea55bbed988f907cebafa61189f45d","tid":1992873,"uid":89349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T11:53:12.000Z","msg":"擺明落你香港人面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZrEZ1hS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZrEZ1hS.png&h=8e451fd0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><im